Package: tidysoilwater
Title: Tidy Tools for Soil Water Retention and Hydraulic Conductivity Modelling
Version: 1.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Einar Emil", "Låker", , "einaremil1999@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0007-5872-4959"))
Description: A tidy reimagining of soil water retention and unsaturated
    hydraulic conductivity modelling. Provides pipe-compatible functions
    that accept and return tibbles, with tidy evaluation support for column
    arguments. Implements the Van Genuchten (1980) soil water retention curve,
    Mualem-Van Genuchten hydraulic conductivity, soil water capacity (dθ/dh),
    soil water diffusivity (D = K/C), and effective saturation. Parameter
    fitting from observed retention data via nonlinear least squares. Supports
    grouped tibbles for multi-pedon workflows and optional parallel fitting
    via parallel::mclapply().
